name: Ricky Iwasaki ye nye esia
title: Kɔmpiutadziɖoɖowo Ŋuti Mɔ̃ɖaŋudɔwɔla
summary: Kɔmpiutadziɖoɖowo Dɔwɔla bibi aɖe, si le mɔnukpɔkpɔ yeye dim be yeawɔ dɔ na dɔ gãwo. Etsɔ ɖe le kɔpi wɔwɔ alo etsɔtsɔ kpe ɖe eŋu me be ame bubuwo nazã. Mexɔe se be nye aɖaŋuwo le sue ne wotsɔe sɔ kple internet, eyata metsɔ ɖe le dɔwɔwɔ kple dɔwɔnu bubuwo, dɔwɔnawo, ɖoɖowɔɖi gbegbɔgblɔwo me ŋutɔ.
